eat to freeze its fur. The hairs then become like needles it can fire."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It lowers its body heat to freeze its fur. The hairs then become like needles it can fire."},{"version":"x","text":"By controlling its body heat, it can freeze the atmosphere around it to make a diamond-dust flurry."},{"version":"y","text":"It lowers its body heat to freeze its fur. The hairs then become like needles it can fire."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"By controlling its body heat, it can freeze the atmosphere around it to make a diamond-dust flurry."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"It lowers its body heat to freeze its fur. The hairs then become like needles it can fire."},{"version":"sun","text":"It can control its body temperature at will. This enables it to freeze the moisture in the atmosphere, creating flurries of diamond dust."},{"version":"moon","text":"It freezes its fur into icicles, spiky and sharp, and tackles its prey."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It protects itself by freezing its fur into sharp needles. It can drop its body temperature below \u201375 degrees Fahrenheit."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It can instantaneously freeze any moisture that\u2019s around it, creating ice pellets to shoot at its prey."},{"version":"sword","text":"Any who become captivated by the beauty of the snowfall that Glaceon creates will be frozen before they know it."},{"version":"shield","text":"The coldness emanating from Glaceon causes powdery snow to form, making it quite a popular Pok\u00e9mon at ski resorts."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Glaceon is able to lower its body temperature very quickly. It freezes the atmosphere, creating diamond dust that glitters like gems while it flutters and dances around."}],"evo":{"name":"eevee","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain"